1
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:09,330
Leave it, I'll do it.

2
00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:11,600
Put this down. Leave it.

3
00:01:12,280 --> 00:01:13,080
Don't worry.

4
00:01:13,960 --> 00:01:14,720
About this matter,

5
00:01:14,720 --> 00:01:16,920
I'll report it clearly to my superiors.

6
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:18,080
I'll be back soon.

7
00:01:18,320 --> 00:01:19,380
There's more here.

8
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:22,200
Be safe on your way.

9
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:25,800
By the way, about what you asked me to investigate,

10
00:01:25,800 --> 00:01:27,160
regarding the troublemaking parents in Dayang Village.

11
00:01:27,160 --> 00:01:28,240
I found some leads.

12
00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:29,320
What leads?

13
00:01:31,440 --> 00:01:32,840
They are villagers of Dayang Village.

14
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:33,920
Mr. and Mrs. Jiang.

15
00:01:34,039 --> 00:01:35,680
They have a daughter named Jiang Xiaomei.

16
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:36,640
Jiang Xiaomei...

17
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:37,840
is quite pretty.

18
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:38,920
And a bit vain.

19
00:01:39,080 --> 00:01:41,720
Later, she applied to be Xiao Tianman's assistant.

20
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:43,360
What Xiao Tianman's assistants do,

21
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:44,400
you know.

22
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:49,360
Are you saying Xiao Tianman kept Jiang Xiaomei for himself?

23
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:54,640
So her disappearance has something to do with him?

24
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:56,360
It's very likely.

25
00:01:58,759 --> 00:02:01,000
Jiang Xiaomei is really...

26
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,200
Enough.

27
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:12,040
Let's go.

28
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:14,800
Okay, I'm leaving.

29
00:02:19,079 --> 00:02:20,079
Do you have a cold?

30
00:02:22,120 --> 00:02:23,200
No, no.

31
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:24,720
Just a little cough.

32
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:26,640
You should go.

33
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:28,400
The mine hasn't been safe lately.

34
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:29,600
You must be careful.

35
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:32,120
I know. Don't worry about me.

36
00:02:34,640 --> 00:02:35,440
I'm off then.

37
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:41,200
I'll be back soon.

38
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:39,200
Mr. Xiao.

39
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:43,320
Ms. Situ, you are truly touching.

40
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:45,680
As a leader of Shanshui Group,

41
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:47,690
you care so much for the people.

42
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:50,600
Visiting every household in Dayang Village.

43
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:53,000
What a coincidence.

44
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:54,290
Why are you here too?

45
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:58,480
After all, the handover isn't complete yet, right?

46
00:03:58,480 --> 00:04:01,010
I'm still the mine manager of Dayang Village.

47
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:02,850
As the mine manager,

48
00:04:02,920 --> 00:04:05,960
caring for the people is part of my job.

49
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:10,200
Then do you know where Mr. and Mrs. Jiang went?

50
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:11,560
I heard they moved.

51
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:12,680
Moved?

52
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:15,200
Their daughter, Jiang Xiaomei,

53
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:17,519
found a good job in another province.

54
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:20,959
So she wanted to take her parents there to enjoy life.

55
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:25,080
Didn't I hear that Jiang Xiaomei went missing?

56
00:04:26,760 --> 00:04:28,480
You must be joking, Ms. Situ.

57
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:32,860
It's the first time I've heard going to another province called missing.

58
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,640
That's good then.

59
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:47,880
Congratulations to Mr. and Mrs. Jiang for enjoying life in the city.

60
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:50,240
Exactly. Unlike us.

61
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:52,720
Still suffering and working hard here.

62
00:04:53,320 --> 00:04:54,200
Don't say that.

63
00:04:54,200 --> 00:04:55,360
Our group came here

64
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:57,840
to stop everyone from suffering.

65
00:04:58,480 --> 00:04:59,400
Including you.

66
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:03,760
Aren't you also leaving soon to enjoy life in the city?

67
00:05:05,320 --> 00:05:06,720
Congratulations, Mr. Xiao.

68
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:07,800
You should prepare well.

69
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,120
Don't wander around for no reason.

70
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:09,840
Let's go.

71
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:12,760
Go.

72
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:22,400
Here come the celebration noodles.

73
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:25,220
Celebration noodles?

74
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:27,160
Isn't Yongzi getting discharged a happy event?

75
00:05:27,160 --> 00:05:29,360
So the noodles we eat are celebration noodles.

76
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:31,560
I thought you two were getting married.

77
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:34,970
It's delicious.

78
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:36,400
Eat slowly. Don't choke.

79
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:39,960
I have to say,

80
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:43,200
Yongzi got the amount and placement of the explosives just right.

81
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:44,240
It was a bad blast,

82
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:46,100
but he recovered pretty quickly.

83
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:51,520
Anyway, let's talk business.

84
00:05:52,159 --> 00:05:53,600
The gold in K26 Gold Mine,

85
00:05:53,640 --> 00:05:55,240
we need to get it out ASAP.

86
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:58,400
The fight between Xiao Tianman and Situ Hongtang is getting worse.

87
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:00,530
We don't have much time left, Brother.

88
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:03,280
By the way, Brother,

89
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:05,720
there are still some explosives left in the mine.

90
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:07,920
Wouldn't blasting be faster?

91
00:06:13,760 --> 00:06:15,040
I know it's illegal,

92
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:16,920
but there seems to be no other way.

93
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,650
Then let's use the explosives.

94
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:44,520
Mom, Dad.

95
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:47,340
I brought Xiaofang to see you.

96
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:49,340
We're doing great.

97
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:52,000
Yongzi, what are you doing here?

98
00:06:56,280 --> 00:06:58,400
What are you doing here, Yang Gaoyong?

99
00:06:58,400 --> 00:07:02,480
Uncle Tian, I brought Xiaofang to pay respects to my parents.

100
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:06,360
You're making such a racket with those firecrackers.

101
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:07,640
Scared the hell out of me.

102
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:10,500
I thought someone was illegally blasting the mine.

103
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,620
Blasting the mine?

104
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:20,720
Uncle Tian, who would dare do that now?

105
00:07:21,200 --> 00:07:24,040
Didn't the authorities strictly ban it?

106
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,570
Isn't it all because of you?

107
00:07:26,960 --> 00:07:27,600
Alright, alright.

108
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:29,400
Stop setting off firecrackers.

109
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,280
Uncle Tian,

110
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:33,120
today is my parents' death anniversary.

111
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:35,120
They both died in a mining accident.

112
00:07:35,440 --> 00:07:37,570
I've been an orphan since I was little.

113
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:43,320
That accident I had a while back,

114
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,760
you know about it.

115
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:46,920
I feel like

116
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:52,920
my parents were watching over me from heaven,

117
00:07:55,360 --> 00:07:59,040
and blessed me to survive the disaster.

118
00:08:02,280 --> 00:08:03,080
So,

119
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:07,080
I brought Xiaofang to pay them proper respects.

120
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:09,720
Yongzi,

121
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:12,690
we all understand your situation.

122
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:15,880
But you're making too big of a scene.

123
00:08:17,520 --> 00:08:19,640
Uncle Tian, please let it slide.

124
00:08:19,640 --> 00:08:20,560
Just this once.

125
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,520
If you're really worried,

126
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:23,800
you can watch from the side.

127
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:25,360
We won't start a fire.

128
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:30,560
Fine, fine.

129
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,620
Thank you, Uncle Tian.

130
00:08:32,640 --> 00:08:33,770
Thanks, Uncle Tian.

131
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:25,220
Thanks for understanding, Uncle Tian. Thanks.

132
00:09:25,320 --> 00:09:26,920
We're from the same village,

133
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:29,080
so we should look out for each other.

134
00:09:31,560 --> 00:09:32,360
Uncle Tian,

135
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:38,320
about Shanshui Group and Situ Hongtang,

136
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:42,680
how do you think they'll change our village?

137
00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:47,520
How would I know? All that reform talk,

138
00:09:48,160 --> 00:09:49,890
I don't understand a word of it.

139
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:53,920
I just hope for a stable job

140
00:09:54,280 --> 00:09:56,320
to feed my wife and kids.

141
00:09:56,400 --> 00:09:59,730
I don't care if it's Xiao Tianman or Situ Hongtang in charge.

142
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:01,200
Yeah.

143
00:10:02,880 --> 00:10:06,280
What we want is simple.

144
00:10:08,760 --> 00:10:11,920
But why is it so hard?

145
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:20,360
Alright, Uncle Tian.

146
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,890
Thanks for understanding.

147
00:10:22,080 --> 00:10:23,210
Uncle Tian, please.

148
00:10:42,080 --> 00:10:43,960
Is this really okay, Brother?

149
00:10:59,880 --> 00:11:00,940
How is it, Brother?

150
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:03,320
Excellent.

151
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:05,640
Is... is this...

152
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:07,320
Does that count as a rich vein?

153
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:08,640
Absolutely.

154
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:10,480
The content is very high.

155
00:11:16,680 --> 00:11:17,480
Who's there?
